00:26:55,300 --> 00:26:56,060
Madam,

579
00:26:56,150 --> 00:26:56,830
I mean, sure,

580
00:26:56,830 --> 00:26:57,870
he owes us some money,

581
00:26:57,870 --> 00:26:59,350
but we shouldn't kill him for that.

582
00:26:59,370 --> 00:27:01,560
Killing someone is against the law.

583
00:27:02,340 --> 00:27:04,340
How would we live afterward?

584
00:27:05,950 --> 00:27:07,030
Oh, so you do know that?

585
00:27:07,030 --> 00:27:07,950
He's so severely injured!

586
00:27:07,950 --> 00:27:08,750
If you throw him out now,

587
00:27:08,750 --> 00:27:09,950
how is that any different from killing him?

588
00:27:09,970 --> 00:27:11,540
Have you lost your conscience?

589
00:27:13,540 --> 00:27:15,030
But that wasn't my idea.

590
00:27:15,030 --> 00:27:16,550
Weren't you the one who instructed earlier

591
00:27:16,550 --> 00:27:17,590
to throw him out

592
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:18,550
when his money runs out?

593
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:19,780
I was just saying that casually!

594
00:27:19,780 --> 00:27:21,110
Can't you just take it lightly?

595
00:27:21,110 --> 00:27:22,150
Did you really have to take it so seriously?

596
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:27,630
We have customers.

597
00:27:27,660 --> 00:27:29,100
Si, we have customers!

598
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:33,350
Dear customers, are you here to stay

599
00:27:33,350 --> 00:27:34,380
or to dine?

600
00:27:34,790 --> 00:27:35,590
To stay.

601
00:27:35,610 --> 00:27:36,620
Four deluxe rooms.

602
00:27:36,870 --> 00:27:37,630
What a coincidence!

603
00:27:37,630 --> 00:27:39,190
Our inn has exactly four deluxe rooms available.

604
00:27:39,190 --> 00:27:40,340
Please come in.

605
00:27:40,780 --> 00:27:41,590
Si!

606
00:27:41,610 --> 00:27:42,480
Take care of their carriage

607
00:27:42,510 --> 00:27:43,310
and feed the horses well!

608
00:27:43,310 --> 00:27:43,910
Got it.

609
00:27:43,910 --> 00:27:44,510
Come in.

610
00:27:44,510 --> 00:27:44,910
Please come in.

611
00:27:44,910 --> 00:27:45,790
San,

612
00:27:45,810 --> 00:27:47,070
take the customers upstairs!

613
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:47,790
Got it.

614
00:27:47,910 --> 00:27:48,510
Come on,

615
00:27:48,510 --> 00:27:49,510
this way, please.

616
00:27:54,590 --> 00:27:56,270
Please come in, dear customers.

617
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:59,030
What do you think?

618
00:27:59,150 --> 00:28:00,030
Are you satisfied?

619
00:28:00,950 --> 00:28:01,750
It's good.

620
00:28:02,150 --> 00:28:04,150
Then I won't disturb your rest.

621
00:28:04,190 --> 00:28:05,000
Hey, buddy.

622
00:28:05,390 --> 00:28:06,540
I'd like to ask you about a place.

623
00:28:06,540 --> 00:28:08,910
Do you know how to get to Orange Lake?

624
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:10,910
This is Orange Lake, right here.

625
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,830
I'm talking about an actual lake,

626
00:28:13,150 --> 00:28:14,270
not our town.

627
00:28:14,950 --> 00:28:15,950
Oh, you mean that lake.

628
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:16,530
Yes.

629
00:28:16,530 --> 00:28:17,740
It's over on the west side of town.

630
00:28:17,740 --> 00:28:18,790
Would you mind

631
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:19,670
showing me the way?

632
00:28:19,670 --> 00:28:20,430
Sure, no problem.

633
00:28:20,630 --> 00:28:21,580
This way, please, sir.

634
00:28:21,950 --> 00:28:23,160
Then I'll go with you.

635
00:28:24,110 --> 00:28:25,270
You should go back to your room and rest.

636
00:28:25,310 --> 00:28:26,830
Zi Fei and Kai Shan will accompany me.

637
00:28:26,940 --> 00:28:27,670
Then...

638
00:28:28,190 --> 00:28:29,430
I'll prepare some food for you

639
00:28:29,430 --> 00:28:30,350
for when you return.

640
00:28:51,070 --> 00:28:51,870
Come in.

641
00:29:00,610 --> 00:29:02,250
I'm Shen Ying, the Foreign Affairs Scribe of Yandu.

642
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,200
Greetings, Mr. Tanghua.

643
00:29:04,910 --> 00:29:05,710
Please, have a seat.

644
00:29:06,710 --> 00:29:07,590
Thank you, Mr. Tanghua.

645
00:29:14,710 --> 00:29:16,990
May I ask why you've

646
00:29:17,190 --> 00:29:18,390
summoned me here?

647
00:29:18,830 --> 00:29:19,710
When I was on the tower ship,

648
00:29:19,710 --> 00:29:21,150
I already told you

649
00:29:21,390 --> 00:29:22,390
that I would come in person

650
00:29:22,390 --> 00:29:23,950
to pay a formal visit to the City Lord of Yandu.

651
00:29:24,290 --> 00:29:27,100
To discuss eliminating the remnants of the War Demons?

652
00:29:27,660 --> 00:29:28,470
That's right.

653
00:29:28,710 --> 00:29:29,510
I have already

654
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:31,750
reported this to the City Lord.

655
00:29:32,230 --> 00:29:34,070
Now that you're here in person,

656
00:29:34,270 --> 00:29:35,830
it is only right that I arrange

657
00:29:35,830 --> 00:29:37,710
a meeting for you as soon as possible.

658
00:29:37,980 --> 00:29:38,830
"It is only right?"

659
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:39,910
Yes.

660
00:29:40,350 --> 00:29:42,260
Unfortunately, the timing is not ideal.

661
00:29:42,630 --> 00:29:45,030
The City Lord is currently in seclusion.

662
00:29:46,260 --> 00:29:47,500
"The timing is not ideal?"

663
00:29:48,130 --> 00:29:49,800
Of all times, he chooses to enter seclusion

664
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:51,350
the moment I arrive?

665
00:29:52,890 --> 00:29:54,240
It really is a coincidence.

666
00:29:54,590 --> 00:29:55,780
But I assure you,

667
00:29:55,810 --> 00:29:57,850
there's no intention to disrespect you.

668
00:29:58,590 --> 00:29:59,390
Fine.

669
00:29:59,740 --> 00:30:01,060
Then I'll wait for him to come out of seclusion.

670
00:30:02,630 --> 00:30:03,750
By the way, Mr. Shen,

671
00:30:04,350 --> 00:30:06,390
have you heard of the Wushuang Society?

672
00:30:10,070 --> 00:30:11,550
Wushuang Society?

673
00:30:13,550 --> 00:30:16,150
I think... I've heard of it.

674
00:30:16,590 --> 00:30:19,070
It should be a guild for craftsmen.

675
00:30:19,690 --> 00:30:21,160
Not just craftsmen, right?

676
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:25,430
I'm afraid I don't understand.

677
00:30:25,470 --> 00:30:27,270
Please enlighten me, Mr. Tanghua.

678
00:30:28,030 --> 00:30:29,460
It seems this Wushuang Society

679
00:30:29,900 --> 00:30:30,910
has connections with many

680
00:30:30,910 --> 00:30:32,710
merchant guilds in Yandu City

681
00:30:33,150 --> 00:30:34,870
and is secretly aiding the War Demons.

682
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:37,070
This... this is impossible!

683
00:30:39,450 --> 00:30:41,050
Mr. Shen, do you really not know,

684
00:30:41,850 --> 00:30:42,970
or are you just pretending not to know?

685
00:30:45,040 --> 00:30:45,840
Mr. Tanghua,

686
00:30:46,230 --> 00:30:47,190
where did you hear

687
00:30:47,190 --> 00:30:48,730
such rumors?

688
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:49,800
This is a serious matter.

689
00:30:49,830 --> 00:30:51,590
We mustn't jump to conclusions based on hearsay.

690
00:30:51,950 --> 00:30:52,710
Without evidence,

691
00:30:52,710 --> 00:30:54,380
how could I make such baseless claims?

692
00:30:55,230 --> 00:30:56,790
The fact that War Demon remnants still exist

693
00:30:56,790 --> 00:30:58,220
is undeniable.

694
00:30:58,630 --> 00:31:00,030
They're hiding and lying low,

695
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:01,670
which means they are struggling to survive.

696
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,820
If no other forces had been lending a hand,

697
00:31:03,910 --> 00:31:05,710
I don't believe they could have remained hidden for so long.

698
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:09,510
Now, the three major races dominate the world.

699
00:31:09,910 --> 00:31:11,230
My Youhu Clan and the War Demons

700
00:31:11,230 --> 00:31:12,920
have an irreconcilable blood feud.

701
00:31:13,470 --> 00:31:15,100
As for who has been aiding them,

702
00:31:15,710 --> 00:31:16,830
isn't that obvious?

703
00:31:18,230 --> 00:31:19,870
Mr. Tanghua, you are mistaken.

704
00:31:20,310 --> 00:31:21,820
The Youhu Clan and the War Demon

705
00:31:21,820 --> 00:31:23,470
indeed have a deep blood feud.

706
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:25,230
But our human race has also suffered greatly

707
00:31:25,230 --> 00:31:26,950
from the War Demon's slaughter and enslavement.

708
00:31:27,390 --> 00:31:28,910
Their atrocities

709
00:31:28,910 --> 00:31:30,150
are deeply etched in our memories.

710
00:31:30,150 --> 00:31:30,830
Our hatred towards them

711
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:32,550
is no less than that of your esteemed clan.

712
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:36,840
This matter must be thoroughly investigated.

713
00:31:37,220 --> 00:31:39,030
We must not let those with ulterior motives

714
00:31:39,030 --> 00:31:40,670
take advantage of this to drive a wedge between us.

715
00:31:40,670 --> 00:31:41,310
Alright.

716
00:31:41,670 --> 00:31:42,430
That's exactly what I was waiting

717
00:31:42,430 --> 00:31:43,630
for you to say.

718
00:31:44,550 --> 00:31:45,830
In the southern part of the city, on Licorice Street,

719
00:31:45,910 --> 00:31:47,310
there's a Green Garden Trading House.

720
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:49,100
Its proprietor is named Lyu Yao.

721
00:31:49,950 --> 00:31:50,790
Come to think of it,

722
00:31:51,070 --> 00:31:52,200
this person was actually brought back

723
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,350
to Yandu City by you.

724
00:31:53,590 --> 00:31:54,400
Is that right?

725
00:31:55,390 --> 00:31:56,180
Yes.

726
00:31:56,620 --> 00:31:58,150
Her father died suddenly,

727
00:31:58,190 --> 00:31:59,990
so she went back home for the funeral.

728
00:32:00,870 --> 00:32:02,350
Then, let's start investigating from here.

729
00:32:03,150 --> 00:32:04,830
She's had two fathers die within three years.

730
00:32:05,150 --> 00:32:07,110
Let's first find out how many fathers she actually has.

731
00:32:27,190 --> 00:32:29,150
Wonderful, wonderful indeed!

732
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:31,990
This melody is like a gift from the heavens.

733
00:32:32,670 --> 00:32:34,630
Dai, I didn't know you had such skill with the zither.

734
00:32:34,870 --> 00:32:36,830
It's truly astonishing.

735
00:32:37,150 --> 00:32:38,220
Just playing around.

736
00:32:39,820 --> 00:32:41,270
Aren't you busy with your official duties today?

737
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:42,710
Though official duties keep me busy,

738
00:32:42,710 --> 00:32:43,710
I can always make time

739
00:32:43,710 --> 00:32:44,680
to see you.

740
00:32:45,870 --> 00:32:46,830
It's strange.

741
00:32:46,950 --> 00:32:48,510
Though I haven't spent much time

742
00:32:48,510 --> 00:32:49,390
with you in this life,

743
00:32:49,630 --> 00:32:51,750
now I find myself thinking of you often.

744
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:54,590
Perhaps this is what they call the bond of family.

745
00:32:55,150 --> 00:32:56,190
That must be it.

746
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:58,550
Before you returned,

747
00:32:58,550 --> 00:32:59,300
I worried every day

748
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:00,710
about Father's seclusion.

749
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:02,350
Sometimes, I couldn't even eat or sleep properly.

750
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:03,750
Now, it's different.

751
00:33:04,110 --> 00:33:05,990
Knowing that you are here in the same place,

752
00:33:06,110 --> 00:33:07,150
my heart

753
00:33:07,270 --> 00:33:08,540
feels much more at ease.

754
00:33:11,030 --> 00:33:12,470
I feel the same way.

755
00:33:13,100 --> 00:33:14,250
I have wandered for half of my life,

756
00:33:14,520 --> 00:33:15,980
only to realize now how precious family is.

757
00:33:18,710 --> 00:33:19,470
Dai, just now,

758
00:33:19,470 --> 00:33:20,590
what piece were you playing?

759
00:33:20,590 --> 00:33:21,740
It was so beautiful.

760
00:33:22,550 --> 00:33:23,470
I don't know either.

761
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:25,590
When Mom taught me,

762
00:33:25,670 --> 00:33:26,830
she never mentioned its name.

763
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:28,490
It was the First Madam who taught you.

764
00:33:31,310 --> 00:33:33,200
But ever since I can remember,

765
00:33:33,710 --> 00:33:35,270
she had always been bedridden.

766
00:33:35,910 --> 00:33:36,790
I'd never

767
00:33:36,790 --> 00:33:38,230
heard her play the zither.

768
00:33:40,630 --> 00:33:41,390
At that time,

769
00:33:41,390 --> 00:33:42,910
she lived in the Yangyu Tower.

770
00:33:43,270 --> 00:33:44,470
Because she couldn't stand the wind,

771
00:33:45,150 --> 00:33:47,070
the doors and windows were always kept closed.

772
00:33:47,590 --> 00:33:49,070
But I often sneaked in there

773
00:33:49,190 --> 00:33:50,780
and got beaten quite some times for it.

774
00:33:51,660 --> 00:33:53,350
Although Father usually doted on me,

775
00:33:53,750 --> 00:33:54,550
he never

776
00:33:54,550 --> 00:33:56,110
held back when punishing me

777
00:33:56,270 --> 00:33:57,870
if I disturbed First Madam's rest.

778
00:33:58,630 --> 00:33:59,780
But even so,

779
00:33:59,950 --> 00:34:01,270
I would still go there often.

780
00:34:01,990 --> 00:34:03,240
I was young at that time

781
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:04,120
and didn't know any better.

782
00:34:04,590 --> 00:34:06,790
I had no self-control when it came to food and drink.

783
00:34:07,430 --> 00:34:09,150
I especially loved sweets.

784
00:34:09,409 --> 00:34:11,130
The whole household kept me in check,

785
00:34:11,429 --> 00:34:12,630
except for the First Madam.

786
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:15,889
Every time I visited, she would give me malt sugar.

787
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:19,239
I still remember clearly

788
00:34:19,270 --> 00:34:20,790
the night when she left this world.

789
00:34:21,679 --> 00:34:22,600
The wind was still,

790
00:34:23,190 --> 00:34:24,150
and the moon was full.

791
00:34:24,989 --> 00:34:25,659
By then,

792
00:34:25,659 --> 00:34:27,230
she could no longer speak.

793
00:34:28,230 --> 00:34:30,270
But she was still happy to see me.

794
00:34:31,750 --> 00:34:34,550
Finally, with trembling hands,

795
00:34:35,230 --> 00:34:36,710
she gave me one last handful of malt sugar.

796
00:34:39,550 --> 00:34:40,350
Dai.

797
00:34:41,670 --> 00:34:42,630
That handful of malt sugar...

798
00:34:44,020 --> 00:34:44,909
was the sweetest thing

799
00:34:44,909 --> 00:34:46,270
I've ever tasted in my life.

800
00:34:53,150 --> 00:34:54,070
Young Lord and Young Mistress,

801
00:34:54,090 --> 00:34:55,610
Shen Ying, Scribe Shen, requests an audience.

802
00:34:56,330 --> 00:34:57,130
Great.

803
00:34:57,570 --> 00:34:58,450
Please invite him in now.

804
00:35:08,620 --> 00:35:10,940
Shen Ying pays his respects to the Young Lord and Young Mistress.

805
00:35:11,430 --> 00:35:12,990
There's no need for such formalities among our own people.

806
00:35:12,990 --> 00:35:13,950
Please, rise quickly.

807
00:35:14,710 --> 00:35:15,590
Thank you, Young Lord.

808
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:19,910
You and your father

809
00:35:19,910 --> 00:35:20,990
have been protecting my elder sister

810
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:22,110
for decades without fail.

811
00:35:22,220 --> 00:35:23,310
This time, not only did you safely

812
00:35:23,310 --> 00:35:24,470
bring her back home,

813
00:35:24,630 --> 00:35:25,830
but you also brought back the medicinal pills.

814
00:35:26,110 --> 00:35:27,750
That is a great merit.

815
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:29,190
So in my heart,

816
00:35:29,190 --> 00:35:30,990
I've long seen you as family.

817
00:35:32,390 --> 00:35:33,750
Thank you for your kindness, Young City Lord.

818
00:35:33,870 --> 00:35:35,590
I dare not accept such an honor.

819
00:35:35,910 --> 00:35:36,950
What are you afraid of?

820
00:35:37,270 --> 00:35:38,430
When Father comes out of seclusion,

821
00:35:38,430 --> 00:35:39,910
he will surely reward you generously.

822
00:35:40,220 --> 00:35:41,510
You must also continue to work hard,

823
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:42,480
not slack off,

824
00:35:42,590 --> 00:35:43,990
and make good use of opportunities.

825
00:35:44,390 --> 00:35:45,190
Yes, Young Lord.

826
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,030
Dai,

827
00:35:47,320 --> 00:35:48,660
I still have official duties to attend to.

828
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:49,880
I'll go take care of them now.

829
00:35:50,270 --> 00:35:51,280
Take care of yourself too.

830
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:52,000
Don't overwork yourself.

831
00:35:52,330 --> 00:35:53,130
I know.

832
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:54,950
Goodbye.

833
00:36:04,790 --> 00:36:05,590
Young Mistress Dai,

834
00:36:05,610 --> 00:36:07,290
Mr. Tanghua has come to Yandu.

835
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:12,260
Where are you gentlemen from?

836
00:36:12,270 --> 00:36:13,000
From the east.

837
00:36:13,890 --> 00:36:15,250
When I was feeding your horses earlier,

838
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:16,950
I noticed that the wheels of your carriage are badly worn.

839
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:18,390
You must have traveled a long way.

840
00:36:19,470 --> 00:36:20,350
I have a friend

841
00:36:20,350 --> 00:36:21,790
who specializes in repairing wheels.

842
00:36:21,790 --> 00:36:23,230
Would you need his services?

843
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:24,350
If needed, I'd be happy to introduce him to you.

844
00:36:24,350 --> 00:36:25,070
If necessary,

845
00:36:25,070 --> 00:36:26,230
we'll certainly trouble you.

846
00:36:26,640 --> 00:36:27,880
How far is it to Orange Lake?

847
00:36:28,670 --> 00:36:29,590
It's right here.

848
00:36:30,950 --> 00:36:32,510
When you mentioned Orange Lake earlier,

849
00:36:32,510 --> 00:36:33,870
it didn't come to me at first.

850
00:36:34,030 --> 00:36:35,230
We locals here

851
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:36,700
all call it Black Dragon Pool.

852
00:36:38,460 --> 00:36:39,710
Why does this lake

853
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:41,070
have two names?

854
00:36:41,470 --> 00:36:43,190
Years ago,

855
00:36:43,470 --> 00:36:44,590
the elders of our town

856
00:36:44,590 --> 00:36:46,110
said they saw a black dragon

857
00:36:46,110 --> 00:36:47,350
coiled above the lake at night.

858
00:36:47,790 --> 00:36:48,830
That's why it's called Black Dragon Pool.

